      <sectiondef kind="func">
      <memberdef kind="function" id="group__xsecure__lms__server__apis_1gad1170a051b711e9dc80db20f6f7e97f2" prot="public" static="yes" const="no" explicit="no" inline="no" virt="non-virtual">
        <type>int</type>
        <definition>static int XSecure_LmsSignVerifyIpi</definition>
        <argsstring>(XPlmi_Cmd *Cmd)</argsstring>
        <name>XSecure_LmsSignVerifyIpi</name>
        <param>
          <type>XPlmi_Cmd *</type>
          <declname>Cmd</declname>
        </param>
        <briefdescription>
<para>This function handler dispatches the request to either XSecure_LmsSignatureVerification (single-tree LMS) or XSecure_HssSignatureVerification (HSS, up to two levels) based on the public key length supplied by the client. </para>        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><verbatim>    PubKeyLen == XSECURE_LMS_PUB_KEY_TOTAL_SIZE      -&gt; LMS
    PubKeyLen == XSECURE_HSS_PUBLIC_KEY_TOTAL_SIZE   -&gt; HSS
</verbatim></para><para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>Cmd</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Pointer to the command structure</para></parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>XST_SUCCESS On successful execution</para></listitem><listitem><para>XSECURE_LMS_INVALID_PARAM If any input parameter is invalid</para></listitem><listitem><para>XST_FAILURE If verification fails </para></listitem></itemizedlist>
</para></simplesect>
</para>        </detaileddescription>
        <inbodydescription>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Validate the size passed by the client matches the expected parameter structure size and is 8-byte aligned</para></listitem><listitem><para>Validate internal address fields in the copied structure</para></listitem><listitem><para>SHA IPI event handling</para></listitem><listitem><para>Set the SHA MODE and start the SHA engine</para></listitem><listitem><para>Dispatch based on public key length:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>LMS single-tree if PubKeyLen == XSECURE_LMS_PUB_KEY_TOTAL_SIZE</para></listitem><listitem><para>HSS multi-tree if PubKeyLen == XSECURE_HSS_PUBLIC_KEY_TOTAL_SIZE</para></listitem></itemizedlist>
</para></listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>        </inbodydescription>
